<html>
  <head>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css" type="text/css" charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg" href="./images/favicon.svg">
    <title>steven kao</title>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@stkao05/layout-grid/src/index.js"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>

  <body>
    <style type="text/css">
      layout-grid {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100vw;
        height: 100vh;
        z-index: 10000;
      }
    </style>

    <h1 class="site-head">steven kao</h1>

    <main>
      <section>
        <p>
        I find great satisfaction building stuff. When I was a kid, the desire for building things was fulfilled with Lego. Now my creative medium is code.
        </p>
        <p>
        My works were centered around the web with a focus on the front end side - an area where the arts of good design and craftsmanships interplay and of which I deep appreciate.
        </p>
        <p>
        My last gig was at Doist, from where I have learned to be a proficient remote worker and had a great pleasure to work on the Todoist app.
        </p>
      </section>
      <section class="info-list mt-2">
        <h2 class="info-list--title">Work</h2>
        <ul class="info-list--list">
        {% for item in works %}
          <li>
            <div>
              {{ item.title }}
            </div>
            <p class="subtext">{{ item.description }}</p>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </section>
      <section class="info-list mt-1">
        <h2 class="info-list--title">Project</h2>
        <ul class="info-list--list">
        {% for project in projects %}
          <li>
            <div>
              <a href="{{ project.link }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ project.title }}</a>
            </div>
            <p class="subtext">{{ project.description }}</p>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
